snippet.textDisplay: The first time I heard this song was at a live concert in the US. It gave me goosebumps... always does! Absolutely fantastic composition. Wish it was available for download on iTunes.  What an amazing coming together of people of different religious backgrounds. Music and performance art has so many examples of this type of brotherhood... how I wish the world at large could learn from it... Also there is something very heartwarming between the chemistry of Salim and Sulaiman... like they are not complete without each other!
